Now, let's define the dependency relationships and calculate the distances. In this case, we'll use a simplified annotation, assuming that we can identify at least the grammatical subject-verb relationships, object-verb relationships, adjective-noun relationships, adverb-verb relationships, etc. Please note that this analysis is done to the best of my ability and might not be entirely accurate.

