5. på -> delade (preposition mark): distance = 1
6. landet -> delade as a direct object: distance = 2
7. ytterligare -> en as an adjective: distance = 1
8. en -> gång as an adjective: distance = 1
9. gång -> delade (no direct head): distance = 4
